SELECT
            f.db_ftxac_txdate AS txdate,
            f.db_ftxac_kinbr  AS kinbr,
            f.db_ftxac_rbrno  AS rbrno,
            f.db_ftxac_aptype AS aptype,
            '"' + left(f.db_ftxac_txcd + replicate(' ', 5),
                       5) + '"'         AS txcd,
            f.db_ftxac_txseq  AS txseq,
            f.db_ftxac_wsno   AS wsno,
            f.db_ftxac_txtno  AS txtno,
            f.db_ftxac_acbrno AS acbrno,
            f.db_ftxac_dept1  AS dept1,
            '"' + left(f.db_ftxac_acno + replicate(' ', 6),
                       6) + '"'         AS acno,
            '"' + left(f.db_ftxac_sbno + replicate(' ', 4),
                       4) + '"'         AS sbno,
            '"' + left(f.db_ftxac_dtlno + replicate(' ', 4),
                       4) + '"'         AS dtlno,
            f.db_ftxac_chkdg  AS chkdg,
            f.db_ftxac_curcd  AS curcd,
            f.db_ftxac_dbcr   AS dbcr,
            f.db_ftxac_amt    AS amt,
            '"' + left(f.db_ftxac_type + replicate(' ', 2),
                       2) + '"'         AS type,
            f.db_ftxac_seqno  AS seqno,
            f.db_ftxac_actfg  AS actfg,
            f.db_ftxac_hcode  AS hcode,
            f.db_ftxac_dmyfg  AS dmyfg,
            f.db_ftxac_txtime AS txtime,
            f.db_ftxac_dept1  AS dept1,
            '"' + left(f.db_ftxac_tlrno + replicate(' ', 2),
                       2) + '"'         AS tlrno,
            '"' + left(f.db_ftxac_supno + replicate(' ', 2),
                       2) + '"'         AS supno,
            f.db_ftxac_rkinbr AS rkinbr,
            '"' + left(f.db_ftxac_refno + replicate(' ', 16),
                       16) + '"'        AS refno,
            '"' + left(f.db_ftxac_docno + replicate(' ', 9),
                       9) + '"'         AS docno,
            '"' + left(f.db_ftxac_cifkey + replicate(' ', 10),
                       10) + '"'        AS cifkey,
            f.db_ftxac_corpno AS corpno,
            f.db_ftxac_opfg   AS opfg,
            f.db_ftxac_charcd AS charcd,
            f.db_ftxac_mbrno  AS mbrno,
            f.db_ftxac_mdept1 AS mdept1,
            '"' + left(f.db_ftxac_macno + replicate(' ', 6),
                       6) + '"'         AS macno,
            '"' + left(f.db_ftxac_msbno + replicate(' ', 4),
                       4) + '"'         AS msbno,
            '"' + left(f.db_ftxac_mdtlno + replicate(' ', 4),
                       4) + '"'         AS mdtlno,
            f.db_ftxac_mchkdg AS mchkdg,
            '"' + left(f.db_ftxac_remark + replicate(' ', 62),
                       62) + '"'        AS remark
        FROM
            botsrdb.db_ftxac_dds f
        WHERE
            f.db_ftxac_txdate = :batchDate
